    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏交流群：630379846</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏介绍：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“灭亡纪元”后的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大部分生物在灾难中被“天使”毁灭，残存的种族于废墟上建立起新的文明。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而随着上一时代的遗物——白匣之柱的衰弱，灾厄即将重演，世界的生命已彻底进入倒计时。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为寻找白匣之柱的消息，得到对抗天灾的方法，探索者少女莉卡驾驶希卡利号前往死海。于是，邂逅了失去记忆的少女缇娜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两位少女，共同踏上了前往白匣之柱的旅途。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她们结识了许多伙伴，也发觉了迫近的危机——吞噬灵魂的天使，神秘的使徒“冰绝”，渴求终末的灰色方舟教团。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >濒临破碎的世界中，两人能否成功抵达白匣之柱，完成对一切的救赎？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——这是无数灰尘，挣扎起舞的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >△丰富的剧情，超40万字文本剧情的游戏流程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >△特色的“领域”机制。每个角色的技能效果都会随着附加不同领域产生变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >△精致的龙骨模型与战斗演出。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >△炼金系统。挑战强敌获取素材，炼成稀有的武器与魔具，增强队伍的实力吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >△强化、魔具技能、天赋技能树、破坏值系统、AP制战斗系统等多种玩法机制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏时长：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30小时以上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>角色介绍：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311310/extras/f1468dbbc49c150ce7f9191ce22c865f.avif?t=1771303317\" width=300 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【缇娜】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作的主人公。失去所有记忆，于死海苏醒的少女。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311310/extras/13a0f32300c1ecab99d049c6a69397f0.avif?t=1771303317\" width=300 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【莉卡】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >B级探索者，希卡利号的船长。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为人正直，遇到需要帮助的人很难袖手旁观。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311310/extras/ee86ba527e10c6f9521c2142aab602cc.avif?t=1771303317\" width=300 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【德蕾斯汀】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有炎之权能的“使徒”，来去如风，令人捉摸不透。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311310/extras/04b17fd02e939c4a213a7e6dfb9a2fe5.avif?t=1771303317\" width=300 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【哈蕾】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >米莱魔法工坊的研究员。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >性格沉稳，彬彬有礼，擅长从绝对理性的角度分析问题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311310/extras/09c0bcf4783a960e60586e18af16bb50.avif?t=1771303317\" width=300 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【拉芙】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A级探索者，被称作“漆黑钢刃”，为追逐“某个人物”而踏上旅途。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311310/extras/57313a6b955a8e36643c5c2f1fb1f94a.avif?t=1771303317\" width=300 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【米洛】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >光之使徒，拥有治愈的权能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311310/extras/f74dea6d56dcd4face03b63371ef7d76.avif?t=1771303317\" width=300 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【？？？】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能够操纵“天灾”死灭雷霆，最为古老与强大的使徒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311310/extras/5848591326aca315fea1628fa9b14ed8.avif?t=1771303317\" width=300 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【露希莉亚】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >前S级最强探索者，莉卡的母亲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因某件事从探索者公会隐退，如今作为莉卡等人的后援而活动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311310/extras/7e57998d22ff8e042b658b701fc0d297.avif?t=1771303317\" width=300 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【杜伽】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >灰色方舟的“圣女”。性格古怪，情绪似乎不太稳定，身上有着某些天使的特征。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311310/extras/346d1289a4fee7d8be5045fe9fa52f38.avif?t=1771303317\" width=300 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【冰绝】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冰之使徒，肆虐整个菲络斯的“人形天灾”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将无数聚集地冰封毁灭，所有人闻之色变的恐怖使徒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
